": 356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans around the world will be surprised to find out that two of America\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most popular sports will not be included in this Summer Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"most popular sports\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"this Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Baseball and softball have been excluded from the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Baseball\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"softball\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Baseball was first included in the Summer Olympic Games back in 1904.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Baseball\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as America\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s favorite pastime, baseball is not only one of the biggest sports in America but in many places all over the world.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"America\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s favorite pastime\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"baseball\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sports\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"many places\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So how could it be excluded from the Games?\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a couple of reasons why \\u00e2\\u0080\\u