 been notoriously one of the best teams in Olympic softball history.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9536232950463503, \"rank\": 0.04388858110614743, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best teams\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic softball history\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a while, they were winning almost everything.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost everything\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This led to softball being excluded from the Olympic Games on more than one occasion.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"softball\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"more than one occasion\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first time it was introduced into the Olympics was back in 1996 but then was excluded again after 2008.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first time\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was brought back again in 2021 and now left out once again.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time baseball and softball were in the Olympics was back in 2021 when both USA teams were defeated by Japan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s baseball and softball teams in the Gold Medal games.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\"